Enter (x) if npc or gem summons a gateway.
Portal Restrictions formated as such: (Ex: NS NR NT LR030 IR QF N)
Coordinates to be formatted without a comma, with uppercase letters (Ex: 24.8S 14.1E)
If portal is accessed via portal gem, enter GW to denote a non fixed location gateway.
If portal is accessed from a dungeon, enter xxxx (Ex: 0008) where xxxx is the landblock ID of the dungeon it is located in.
